Packages 
Package Description
ohos.ivi.drivingsafety
Provides driving management and control functions.
ohos.ivi.drivingsafety.model
Provides result information of the driving control policy.
ohos.ivihardware
Provides interfaces related to vehicle service connectivity.
ohos.ivihardware.adas
Provides signal access functions dedicated to Advanced Driver Assistant System (ADAS), including the retrieval, setting, subscription, and unsubscription of basic ADAS information and driving and parking.
ohos.ivihardware.adas.model
Provides abstract classes about Advanced Driver Assistant System (ADAS) callbacks and basic data types.
ohos.ivihardware.advancedmanager
Provides classes that contain advanced methods for vehicle control and Advanced Driver Assistant System (ADAS).
ohos.ivihardware.cluster
Provides signal access functions dedicated to clusters, including cluster property definition, sensor value retrieval and subscription, and actuator value retrieval, setting, and subscription.
ohos.ivihardware.cluster.model
Provides abstract classes about cluster control callback and basic data types.
ohos.ivihardware.model
Provides abstract callback interfaces and service name enumerations required for vehicle service connectivity.
ohos.ivihardware.tbox
Provides signal access functions dedicated to Telematics Box (T-Box), including the retrieval, setting, subscription, and unsubscription of XCall and battery charging signal values.
ohos.ivihardware.tbox.model
Provides abstract classes about Telematics Box (T-Box) callbacks and basic data types.
ohos.ivihardware.vehiclecontrol
Provides signal access functions dedicated to vehicles, including vehicle property definition, sensor value retrieval and subscription, and actuator value retrieval, setting, and subscription.
ohos.ivihardware.vehiclecontrol.model
Provides abstract classes about vehicle control callback and basic data types.
ohos.multimedia.radio
Provides configurations of radio attributes.
ohos.multimedia.radio.kitsimpl
Provides all the implementation classes required for the radio service.
ohos.multimedia.radio.model
Provides custom callbacks for the radio service.
